{"tid":576893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夕爺話你知，點解連登仔覺得全部女人都係臭雞","createTime":"2018-03-01T09:36:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-01T12:43:15.000Z","uid":161646,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c88dd34cd5a408066a7e25641d2a4d819176c9e","tid":576893,"uid":161646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"想你太傷 不會設想<br />\n再懷念變孽障<br />\n就絕到亂誣蔑你醜樣<br />\n毀懷形象<br />\n因你受了傷 憎你會有獎<br />\n想到缺點便拍掌<br />\n不要讓我面對真相<br />\n我毒到騷癢<br />\n恨才能令我輕傷<br />\n不能懷念臭雞<br />\n不如懷恨臭雞<br />\n恨人亦要花氣力<br />\n例如恨你 為人自私也任性<br />\n我憎你不停來為我<br />\n添加大量情敵<br />\n將鹹甜回憶<br />\n記恨你才能<br />\n令愛著你也沒價值<br />\n直到令我的強烈愛意平息<br />\n我愛臭雞 我怕臭雞<br />\n厭惡你方能夠不難過<br />\n憎你那過錯 憎你放棄我<br />\n再愛你嫌命長麼<br />\n不能懷念愛惜<br />\n不如懷恨更激<br />\n恨人亦要花氣力<br />\n恨完就怕 如情隨宣洩絕跡<br />\n不停來為我添加大量情敵<br />\n憎 完全被迫<br />\n記恨你才能<br />\n令愛著你也沒價值<br />\n直到令我的強烈愛意平息"},{"pid":"5d567515f260e4b1882d5c933d2be1bd9bdcf16c","tid":576893,"uid":15419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},{"pid":"05a1c7b2d0850e070a361c9ab44ebb11fde03482","tid":576893,"uid":161646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d567515f260e4b1882d5c933d2be1bd9bdcf16c","tid":576893,"uid":15419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T09:42:54.000Z","msg":"唔好笑"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T12:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c9e2369b2d90d0cdfe44652f3e7348fa8d4f0e","tid":576893,"uid":168161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T12:42:16.000Z","msg":"咩黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9d20a877e209cc9fc98b7acf03affdb23b79e0","tid":576893,"uid":61465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89c9e2369b2d90d0cdfe44652f3e7348fa8d4f0e","tid":576893,"uid":168161,"li